<P><MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="1a">The firste tretis of surgerie halt wi&thorn;inne him general ruelis &amp; |canones, &amp; ha&thorn; .iij. techingis /  &THORN;e firste techinge of &thorn;e firste tretis,|ha&thorn; &thorn;re chapitlis.  &para; Cap. j. of &thorn;e first tretis of &thorn;e firste techynge|is of definiciones &amp; of parties &thorn;at ben sugettis to surgerie /  Cap. ij.|is of &thorn;e qualite, foorme &amp; maners of a surgien /  &para; Cap. iij. is of|intencioun of a surgien / The secunde techynge of &thorn;e first tretis|is on summe &amp; oon chapitle of anotomie, &amp; &thorn;at is to seie: &thorn;e|knouleche of &thorn;e foorme, &amp; &thorn;e complexciouns, &amp; &thorn;e helpingis of|alle &thorn;e senews, veines, grustlis, brawnis, guttis, bladdre, lyuere,|milte, &amp; alle o&thorn;ere synguler lymes, &amp; of &thorn;e engendringe of &thorn;e child|in &thorn;e modir wombe / The first<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>first,</I> mistake for <I>&thorn;ridde,</I> as below.</NOTE> techinge of &thorn;e first tretis ha&thorn;|.xv. chapitlis /
<LIST>
<ITEM>&para; Cap. j. of &thorn;e &thorn;ridde techinge of &thorn;e .j.<NOTE PLACE="foot">Chafed: not room for <I>first.</I></NOTE> tretis <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="1b">is of a comoun |word of woundis, &amp; olde woundis / p. 31</ITEM>
<ITEM>
