<P>The secunde tretis is of particuler woundis of alle lymes of office|from &thorn;e heed to the foot, techinge &thorn;e anotomie of alle lymes|from &thorn;e heed to &thorn;e foot, &thorn;at happi&thorn; to be woundid; &amp; &thorn;ou haddist| tofore &thorn;e anatomie <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="2a">of veynes &amp; senewis, &amp; o&thorn;ere smale lymes.
<PB N="3">|And so whanne &thorn;is tretis is ful eendid, &thorn;ou hast anotamie of alle|lymes of &thorn;i bodi, &amp; &thorn;is tretis vndir oon summe conteyne&thorn; x.|chapitlis.
