<P>&THORN;is maner siknes <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="170a">schal be helid wi&thorn; phisic or it be confermed.|&amp; whanne it is confermed, it mote be curid wi&thorn; a mannes hand.|&THORN;e patient mote absteine him fro sopers<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>soper,</I> c&oelig;na. See Skeat, <I>Et. Dict.</I>, s. v. supper.</NOTE> &amp; fro al maner fatte|potagis, &amp; from al maner moiste fruitis, &amp; fro al maner fruitis &thorn;at|engendri&thorn; moistnes / saue he schal vse hote &thorn;ingis, &amp; he schal ofte|be purgid wi&thorn; pillis cochie rasis, &thorn;at is &thorn;e beste &thorn;ing laxatif &thorn;at|mai be for i&yogh;en, &amp; &thorn;an make a collirie of gallis of beestis &thorn;at is|maad in &thorn;is maner. &rx;, fellis grue, fellis stelionis, fellis hirci, fellis|anticipitris,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>anticipiter,</I> med. Lat. for <I>accipiter.</I> Dufr. Glass.</NOTE> fellis aquile &amp; perdicis, &amp; alle &thorn;ese gallis ben drie, &amp;|take herof .x. partijs, euforbie, colloquintide, ana. partem .j, grinde|all &thorn;ese &amp; tempere hem wi&thorn; &thorn;e iuys of fenigreci &amp; make &thorn;erof|pelottis. &amp; whanne &thorn;ou wolt worche &thorn;erwi&thorn;, resolue oon &thorn;erof wi&thorn;|water of fenel distillid, &amp; leie it in his i&yogh;e twies on &thorn;e day ./|&para; Ano&thorn;er li&yogh;t medicyn &thorn;at is preued / Take askis of vynes &amp;|sarce hem &amp; make &thorn;erof lie with good whit wijn, &amp; lete it stonde|in a glasen vessel, &amp; lete it clarifie &thorn;erinne. &amp; &thorn;is is a good collirie|&thorn;erfore, for &thorn;e more cold &thorn;at cataracta is, &thorn;e bettir &thorn;is medicyn is|&thorn;erfore / And if cataracta be <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="170b">so confermed &thorn;at it stoppe al &thorn;e|li&yogh;t, &thorn;an it is incurable wi&thorn; medicyns, &amp; also &thorn;er ben manie o&thorn;ere|incurable. &para; And if it so be &thorn;at he se not, &thorn;an make him close|his i&yogh;en togidere, &amp; frote al sof