erijs a&yogh;en, &amp; in &thorn;is maner &thorn;ou schalt worche wi&thorn; &thorn;i|cauterijs.  &para; ffor manie men maki&thorn; oon cauterie or .ij, &amp; if &thorn;ei seen|&thorn;at it profiti&thorn; not, &thorn;an &thorn;ei leeue&thorn; of &amp; worchi&thorn; nomore.  &amp; manie|men contynuede &thorn;eron til &thorn;e pacient be brou&yogh;t al doun &amp; li&yogh;tli|deed / &amp; in &thorn;is maner ne schulde not a leche worche / ffor G. sei&thorn;:|it is a feble leche, &thorn;at can not helpe &thorn;at is able to be holpen.  &amp;|defaute herof is &thorn;is: &thorn;at manie lechis &yogh;eue&thorn; medicyns, &amp; ne maki&thorn;|no space to bringe &thorn;e patient into good staat a&yogh;en<NOTE PLACE="foot">Add. 26,106, fol. 93: si plus dant, non interponunt spacium nutriendi.</NOTE> / Alle &thorn;ese rulis|&thorn;at G. sei&thorn; &thorn;ou schalt attende in &thorn;is maner: if &thorn;e patient be maad|feble wi&thorn; medicyns laxatiuis &amp; wi&thorn; cauterijs, &thorn;an &thorn;ou cesse of &thorn;i|medicyns &amp; &yogh;eue him comfortatif metis &amp; drinkis for to releue him|a&yogh;en, &amp; &thorn;an &thorn;ou mi&yogh;t worche wi&thorn; &thorn;i medicyns a&yogh;en. &amp; &thorn;us &thorn;ou mi&yogh;t|do perfitly &thorn;e cure / And heron manie men erri&thorn; &thorn;at ben holden ful|kunnyng / <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="226b">&amp; &thorn;erfore I haue sett it in &thorn;is place &thorn;at it mowe be |ensaumple to &thorn;ee / Also &thorn;ou schalt make a cauterie vpon rotid|fleisch, til &thorn;ou haue take awei al &thorn;e corrupcioun &thorn;erof.  &amp; in &thorn;is caas|we mowen vse hoot feruent oile for to springe vpon &thorn;e corrupcioun,
