<DIV3 TYPE="chapter" N="6">
<HEAD>&para; Of medicyns cauteratiuis &amp; corrosiuis /</HEAD>
<P>Corosiuis &amp; cauteri&yogh;atiuis we vsi&thorn; in cirurgie in manie causis,|&amp; of corosiuis summe ben feble, &amp; summe ben strong, &amp;|summe be&thorn; more stronger / These ben feble, hermodactilis, aristologia,|brionia, gencina,<NOTE PLACE="foot">Lat.: gentiana.</NOTE> vitriolum adustum, &amp; &thorn;ese haue&thorn; moost|vertu in moist bodies.  &para; More strong ben &thorn;es: vitriolum not combustum,|tapsia, pees milui,<NOTE PLACE="foot">MS. <I>vulpi</I>.  Pes milui "crow-foot."</NOTE> <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="263a">apium rampnum,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Alphita</I>, p. 11: "<I>Apium ranarum</I> siue <I>apium rampnum</I> crescit in|pratis ..."  See <I>rampinus</I>, uncus.&mdash;Dufr.</NOTE> cortex viticelle<NOTE PLACE="foot">Wr. W&uuml;l., 138, 28: "Viticella, wi&thorn;winde."</NOTE> / And |&thorn;ese ben more strong: flos eris, viride eris, es vstum, arsenicum,|sulphur.  &para; Also &thorn;ese ben more strong: calx viua maad of stoonis,|&amp; of schellis of eiren &amp; oistris, &amp; strong lye, &amp; arsenicum sublimatum,|&amp; watir maad of &thorn;ese &thorn;ingis; &amp; of &thorn;ese medicyns &thorn;ou mi&yogh;t|make medicyns bo&thorn;e simple &amp; compound, whiche &thorn;ou mi&yogh;t vse|whanne &thorn;ou wolt take awei deed fleisch, more strong &amp; lasse strong|as &thorn;ou seest &thorn;at it is nede &thorn;erto.  &para; Of medicins &thorn;at ben compound|I wole telle &thorn;ee a fewe, for of simple medicyns &thorn;ou mi&yogh;t|compound manie.  &para; A poudre &thorn;at wi&thorn;outen ony greuaunce &amp;|li&yogh;tli freti&thorn; awei deed fleisch / &rx;, viride eris, hermodactulorum,|aristologia rotunda, make &thorn;erof poudre &amp; kepe it in a drie place, &amp;|whanne &thorn;ou wolt do awei deed fleisch / Take lynet ei&thorn;er lynnen|cloo&thorn;, &amp; wete it with &thorn;i spotil &amp; leie it in &thorn;e poudre, &amp; turne it vp|&amp; doun, &amp; leie it vpon &thorn;e place.  &para; Thou schalt attende superfluite|of fleisch<NOTE PLACE