<PB N="355">|an ende of &thorn;is book.  &amp; ful ofte I haue bede goddis grace &thorn;erto /|wherfore god ha&thorn; grauntid, &amp; god for his blessid name blesse &thorn;is|book &amp; alle werkis &thorn;at ben wrou&yogh;t in his name / <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="269b">And god for his |miche grace lete hem wel worche &thorn;at taki&thorn; &thorn;is werk on honde, &amp;|bringe errouris out of her herte, &amp; bringe hem &amp; us to a good|ende / To &thorn;e worschip of his blessid name &amp; profit of his seruauntis,|&amp; me to for&yogh;euenes of my synnes, god it graunte et imperat|per omnia secula seculorum AmeN.</P>
